                        td
                            div.btn.btn-default(bx-name='components/popover' data-placement='left' data-align='top' data-title='placement left + align top' data-content='Remember what is unbecoming to do is also unbecoming to speak of.') 位于左侧 + 顶部对齐
                            div.btn.btn-default(bx-name='components/popover' data-placement='bottom' data-align='right' data-title='placement bottom + align right' data-content='Remember what is unbecoming to do is also unbecoming to speak of.') 位于下方 + 右侧对齐
                    tr
                        td
                            div.btn.btn-default(bx-name='components/popover' data-placement='right' data-align='middle' data-title='placement right + align middle' data-content='Remember what is unbecoming to do is also unbecoming to speak of.') 位于右侧 + 垂直居中对齐
                        td -
