                        td
                            div.btn.btn-default(bx-name='components/popover' data-placement='top' data-align='right' data-title='placement top + align right' data-content='Remember what is unbecoming to do is also unbecoming to speak of.') 位于上方 + 右侧对齐
                            div.btn.btn-default(bx-name='components/popover' data-placement='left' data-align='bottom' data-title='placement left + align bottom' data-content='Remember what is unbecoming to do is also unbecoming to speak of.') 位于左侧 + 底部对齐
        div
            h3.fontsize-16 如果浮层中的内容很复杂，例如多层嵌套的 HTML 代码，或者是含有 <code>&lt;pre&gt;</code>代码，建议预先在页面中渲染好浮层中的内容，并设置一个 <code>id</code> 属性，然后在组件上设置 <code>template: #id</code>。
            <div id="escaped" class="popover top">
                <div class="arrow"></div>
                <div class="popover-content">
                    <div>&lt;div&gt;</div>
                    <pre>&lt;div&gt;</pre>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div bx-name="components/popover" data-placement="top" data-template="#escaped" data-width="200" class="btn btn-default">Code</div>
        //- 启动
        script.
            require(['brix/loader', 'jquery', 'highlightjs'], function(Loader, $, hljs) {
                window.Loader = Loader
                Loader.boot(function() {
                    $('iframe', top.document).height($(document.body).outerHeight())
                    $(document.body).find('pre code').each(function(index, code) {
                        hljs.highlightBlock(code)
                    })
                    var instances = Loader.query('components/colorpicker')
                })
            })
